name: Api\Response\Channel
description: See the fields returned by the read channel endpoint.

properties.name: createdAt
properties.description: The date and time the channel was created.

properties.name: id
properties.description: The unique identifier of the channel.

properties.name: modifiedAt
properties.description: The date and time the channel was last modified.

properties.name: shareUrl
properties.description: The URL to the channel within the News app. The shareUrl field applies only on devices with iOS 9 installed.

properties.name: website
properties.description: The website that corresponds to this channel.
